{"ja502:0.1":"Jataka ","ja502:0.2":"Visatinipata ","ja502:0.3":"Matangavagga ","ja502:0.4":"6. Culahamsajataka ","ja502:1.1":"“Ete hamsa pakkamanti, ","ja502:1.2":"vakkanga bhayamerita; ","ja502:1.3":"Harittaca hemavanna, ","ja502:1.4":"kamam sumukha pakkama. ","ja502:2.1":"Ohaya mam natigana, ","ja502:2.2":"ekam pasavasam gatam; ","ja502:2.3":"Anapekkhamana gacchanti, ","ja502:2.4":"kim eko avahiyyasi. ","ja502:3.1":"Pateva patatam settha, ","ja502:3.2":"natthi baddhe sahayata; ","ja502:3.3":"Ma anighaya hapesi, ","ja502:3.4":"kamam sumukha pakkama”. ","ja502:4.1":"“Naham ‘dukkhapareto’ti, ","ja502:4.2":"dhatarattha tuvam jahe; ","ja502:4.3":"Jivitam maranam va me, ","ja502:4.4":"taya saddhim bhavissati”. ","ja502:5.1":"“Etadariyassa kalyanam, ","ja502:5.2":"yam tvam sumukha bhasasi; ","ja502:5.3":"Tanca vimamsamanoham, ","ja502:5.4":"‘patatetam’ avassajim”. ","ja502:6.1":"“Apadena padam yati, ","ja502:6.2":"antalikkhacaro dijo; ","ja502:6.3":"Ara pasam na bujjhi tvam, ","ja502:6.4":"hamsanam pavaruttama”. ","ja502:7.1":"“Yada parabhavo hoti, ","ja502:7.2":"poso jivitasankhaye; ","ja502:7.3":"Atha jalanca pasanca, ","ja502:7.4":"asajjapi na bujjhati”. ","ja502:8.1":"“Ete hamsa pakkamanti, ","ja502:8.2":"vakkanga bhayamerita; ","ja502:8.3":"Harittaca hemavanna, ","ja502:8.4":"tvanneva avahiyyasi. ","ja502:9.1":"Ete bhutva ca pitva ca, ","ja502:9.2":"pakkamanti vihangama; ","ja502:9.3":"Anapekkhamana vakkanga, ","ja502:9.4":"tvanneveko upasasi. ","ja502:10.1":"Kim nu tyayam dijo hoti, ","ja502:10.2":"mutto baddham upasasi; ","ja502:10.3":"Ohaya sakuna yanti, ","ja502:10.4":"kim eko avahiyyasi”. ","ja502:11.1":"“Raja me so dijo mitto, ","ja502:11.2":"sakha panasamo ca me; ","ja502:11.3":"Neva nam vijahissami, ","ja502:11.4":"yava kalassa pariyayam”. ","ja502:12.1":"“Yo ca tvam sakhino hetu, ","ja502:12.2":"panam cajitumicchasi; ","ja502:12.3":"So te sahayam muncami, ","ja502:12.4":"hotu raja tavanugo”. ","ja502:13.1":"“Evam luddaka nandassu, ","ja502:13.2":"saha sabbehi natibhi; ","ja502:13.3":"Yathahamajja nandami, ","ja502:13.4":"muttam disva dijadhipam”. ","ja502:14.1":"“Kaccinnu bhoto kusalam, ","ja502:14.2":"kacci bhoto anamayam; ","ja502:14.3":"Kacci ratthamidam phitam, ","ja502:14.4":"dhammena manusasasi”. ","ja502:15.1":"“Kusalanceva me hamsa, ","ja502:15.2":"atho hamsa anamayam; ","ja502:15.3":"Atho ratthamidam phitam, ","ja502:15.4":"dhammena manusasaham”. ","ja502:16.1":"“Kacci bhoto amaccesu, ","ja502:16.2":"doso koci na vijjati; ","ja502:16.3":"Kacci ara amitta te, ","ja502:16.4":"chaya dakkhinatoriva”. ","ja502:17.1":"“Athopi me amaccesu, ","ja502:17.2":"doso koci na vijjati; ","ja502:17.3":"Atho ara amitta me, ","ja502:17.4":"chaya dakkhinatoriva”. ","ja502:18.1":"“Kacci te sadisi bhariya, ","ja502:18.2":"assava piyabhanini; ","ja502:18.3":"Puttarupayasupeta, ","ja502:18.4":"tava chandavasanuga”. ","ja502:19.1":"“Atho me sadisi bhariya, ","ja502:19.2":"assava piyabhanini; ","ja502:19.3":"Puttarupayasupeta, ","ja502:19.4":"mama chandavasanuga”. ","ja502:20.1":"“Kacci te bahavo putta, ","ja502:20.2":"sujata ratthavaddhana; ","ja502:20.3":"Pannajavena sampanna, ","ja502:20.4":"sammodanti tato tato”. ","ja502:21.1":"“Satameko ca me putta, ","ja502:21.2":"dhatarattha maya suta; ","ja502:21.3":"Tesam tvam kiccamakkhahi, ","ja502:21.4":"navarujjhanti te vaco”. ","ja502:22.1":"“Upapannopi ce hoti, ","ja502:22.2":"jatiya vinayena va; ","ja502:22.3":"Atha paccha kurute yogam, ","ja502:22.4":"kicche apasu sidati. ","ja502:23.1":"Tassa samhirapannassa, ","ja502:23.2":"vivaro jayate maha; ","ja502:23.3":"Rattimandhova rupani, ","ja502:23.4":"thulani manupassati. ","ja502:24.1":"Asare sarayogannu, ","ja502:24.2":"matim na tveva vindati; ","ja502:24.3":"Sarabhova giriduggasmim, ","ja502:24.4":"antarayeva sidati. ","ja502:25.1":"Hinajaccopi ce hoti, ","ja502:25.2":"utthata dhitima naro; ","ja502:25.3":"Acarasilasampanno, ","ja502:25.4":"nise aggiva bhasati. ","ja502:26.1":"Etam me upamam katva, ","ja502:26.2":"putte vijjasu vacaya; ","ja502:26.3":"Samvirulhetha medhavi, ","ja502:26.4":"khette bijamva vutthiya”ti. ","ja502:27.1":"Culahamsajatakam chattham. "}